## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:batchai:Experiment demo_experiment /subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/resourceGroups/demo_resource_group/providers/Microsoft.BatchAI/workspaces/demo_workspace/experiments/demo_experiment 
```
